</div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column_inner fusion-builder-nested-column-1 fusion_builder_column_inner_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:3.84%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:32px;--awb-spacing-left-large:3.84%;--awb-width-medium:50%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:3.84%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:3.84%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div id="cta-form" class="_form_35"></div><script type="rocketlazyloadscript" data-rocket-src="https://sandaybv.activehosted.com/f/embed.php?id=35" data-rocket-type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8" data-rocket-defer defer></script></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-9 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-top:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-justify-content-center fusion-flex-content-wrap" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-13 fusion_builder_column_4_5 4_5 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:80%;--awb-margin-top-large:8%;--awb-spacing-right-large:2.4%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:32px;--awb-spacing-left-large:2.4%;--awb-width-medium:80%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:2.4%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:2.4%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-menu-anchor" id="nieuws"></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-margin-top:0px;--awb-margin-right:0px;--awb-margin-bottom:60px;--awb-margin-left:0px;--awb-margin-top-small:0px;--awb-margin-right-small:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-small:24px;--awb-margin-left-small:0px;"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" style="margin:0;--fontSize:72;line-height:1.2;">Bekijk het laatste nieuws</h2></div><div class="swiper slider-wrapper v1" id="nieuws"><div class="slider-container swiper-wrapper"><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/persoonlijke-hybride-zorg-in-de-apotheek-met-kijksluiter-medicijnwijs/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">17-03-2026</small><h3>Persoonlijke, hybride zorg in de apotheek met KIJKsluiter & MedicijnWijs</h3><p>De balie is druk, vragen stapelen zich snel op en medicatie wordt steeds complexer. Juist daarom is het belangrijker dan ooit om je tijd slim te verdelen. En dat kan met hybride zorg!</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1536" height="840" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pha23HncUqNO-pqbvs527trI7crmi-2.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pha23HncUqNO-pqbvs527trI7crmi-2-300x164.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pha23HncUqNO-pqbvs527trI7crmi-2-768x420.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pha23HncUqNO-pqbvs527trI7crmi-2-1024x560.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Pha23HncUqNO-pqbvs527trI7crmi-2.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px" /></div></a><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/samen-met-mosadex-bouwen-we-verder/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">02-03-2026</small><h3>Samen met Mosadex bouwen we verder</h3><p>We zetten een volgende stap in hoe Sanday Apotheek en Mosadex op elkaar aansluiten.</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1097" height="600" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Mosadex-Sanday-5.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Mosadex-Sanday-5-300x164.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Mosadex-Sanday-5-768x420.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Mosadex-Sanday-5-1024x560.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Mosadex-Sanday-5.png 1097w" sizes="(max-width: 1097px) 100vw, 1097px" /></div></a><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/nieuwe-schermen-in-sanday-apotheek-slimmer-sneller-en-overzichtelijker/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">04-12-2025</small><h3>Nieuwe schermen in Sanday Apotheek: slimmer, sneller en overzichtelijker</h3><p>Je hebt het misschien al gemerkt: stap voor stap maken we jouw schermen frisser in Sanday Apotheek. En dat doen we niet alleen, maar samen met onze pilotapotheken.</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1346" height="706" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Nieuwe-schermen-1.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Nieuwe-schermen-1-300x157.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Nieuwe-schermen-1-768x403.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Nieuwe-schermen-1-1024x537.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Nieuwe-schermen-1.png 1346w" sizes="(max-width: 1346px) 100vw, 1346px" /></div></a><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/chantal-en-monique-van-apotheekbalie-naar-accountmanager/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">27-11-2025</small><h3>Chantal en Monique: van apotheekbalie naar accountmanager</h3><p>Van de apotheek naar sales: Chantal en Monique hadden het nooit verwacht. Toch is hun achtergrond precies wat hen zo goed maakt in hun rol bij Sanday.</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1884" height="1028" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Chantal-en-Monique.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Chantal-en-Monique-300x164.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Chantal-en-Monique-768x419.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Chantal-en-Monique-1024x559.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Chantal-en-Monique.png 1884w" sizes="(max-width: 1884px) 100vw, 1884px" /></div></a><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/hoe-huisartsenpraktijk-de-stadswal-alles-omgooide-en-beter-uitkwam/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">28-10-2025</small><h3>Huisartsenpraktijk de Stadswal gooide alles om en kwam beter uit</h3><p>Een nieuw pand. Een nieuw HIS. Nieuwe routines, nieuwe werkplekken. Voor huisartsenpraktijk de Stadswal was 2024 hét moment om alles om te gooien.</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1536" height="840" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Stadswal.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Stadswal-300x164.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Stadswal-768x420.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Stadswal-1024x560.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Stadswal.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px" /></div></a><a href="https://sanday.com/nieuws/hr-adviseur-aimee-over-werkplezier-blij-medewerkers-maken-een-blije-organisatie/" class="swiper-slide"><div class="inner-left"><small class="date" style="margin-bottom:8px;">28-08-2025</small><h3>Volgens HR-adviseur Aimee zit het zo: blije mensen = blije organisatie</h3><p>Soms ben je wel veertig uur per week op je werk. Dan mag het ook een fijne plek zijn, vindt Aimee. Dáár zet ze zich als HR-adviseur elke dag voor in.</p></div><div class="inner-right"><img decoding="async" width="1097" height="600" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Aimee-4.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Aimee-4-300x164.png 300w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Aimee-4-768x420.png 768w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Aimee-4-1024x560.png 1024w, https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Aimee-4.png 1097w" sizes="(max-width: 1097px) 100vw, 1097px" /></div></a></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div><div id="nieuws-prev" class="swiper-button-prev swiper-nav-button"></div><div id="nieuws-next" class="swiper-button-next swiper-nav-button"></div></div><div style="text-align:center;"><a class="fusion-button button-flat fusion-button-default-size button-default fusion-button-default button-2 fusion-button-default-span fusion-button-default-type" style="--awb-margin-top:70px;" target="_self" href="/nieuws/"><span class="fusion-button-text awb-button__text awb-button__text--default">Bekijk meer</span></a></div></div></div></div></div>
<div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-10 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-overflow:visible;--awb-padding-bottom:128px;--awb-background-color:var(--awb-color5);--awb-background-image:linear-gradient(180deg, #2d333e 0%,#908cc3 100%);--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap" style="width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-14 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-overflow:visible;--awb-bg-color:rgba(255,255,255,0);--awb-bg-color-hover:rgba(255,255,255,0);--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:32px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-9 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-text-color:#ffffff;--awb-margin-top:0px;--awb-margin-right:0px;--awb-margin-left:0px;--awb-margin-top-small:0px;--awb-margin-right-small:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-small:24px;--awb-margin-left-small:0px;"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" style="margin:0;--fontSize:72;line-height:1.2;">Klantverhalen</h2></div><div class="swiper slider-wrapper v1" id="klantverhalen"><div class="slider-container swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="350" height="350" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jannie-Lap.webp" alt="Jannie Lap - Huisartsenpraktijk Boom en Driece"/><p>“Heel eerlijk? Ik zag er als een berg tegenop, maar uiteindelijk heb ik me echt druk gemaakt om niks! Je zit er zó in", en ze knipt met haar vingers.</p><h4>Jannie Lap - Huisartsenpraktijk Boom en Driece</h4></div><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="500" height="500" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jasper-cords.webp" alt="Jasper Cords - Doornse Apotheek B.V"/><p>"Ik zou niet graag meer in een apotheek willen werken waar ze geen Sanday hebben. Nu houd je meer tijd over. Zo kan je nog een keer iets checken, of langer de tijd nemen voor een patiënt. En naar mijn mening verbetert dat, samen met de kans op minder fouten, zeker de kwaliteit van de zorg.”</p><h4>Jasper Cords - Doornse Apotheek B.V</h4></div><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="350" height="350" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gerjanne.webp" alt="Gerjanne - Huisartsenpraktijk Boom en Driece"/><p>"Sanday vroeg ons naar onze wensen en naar de manier waarop we in de praktijk werken. Toen gaf ik mijn ideeën, en die zitten nu in Sanday! Zo fijn dat er zo goed naar onze wensen wordt geluisterd. En dat het dan ook echt gebeurt!"

<span data-teams="true"><span class="ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak" dir="ltr"> </span></span></p><h4>Gerjanne - Huisartsenpraktijk Boom en Driece</h4></div><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="350" height="350" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bas-Albers.webp" alt="Bas Albers - Apotheek Albers"/><p>Mijn apotheek groeide in korte tijd met 20%, maar mijn wachttijden bleven hetzelfde. Dat komt door het gebruiksgemak, de efficiëntie en dat alle gegevens digitaal beschikbaar zijn. Ook kan ik overal inloggen. Hierdoor schakel ik snel op afstand en heb ik altijd controle over wat er in de apotheek gebeurt.</p><h4>Bas Albers - Apotheek Albers</h4></div><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="350" height="350" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mudassar-Aslam.webp" alt="Mudassar Aslam - Apotheek Drechterland"/><p>Het grootste voordeel van Sanday is hoe efficiënt het hele platform is. We hoeven niet meer door verschillende menu's te navigeren of van tabblad te wisselen. Hierdoor verzetten we méér werk met hetzelfde aantal medewerkers”</p><h4>Mudassar Aslam - Apotheek Drechterland</h4></div><div class="swiper-slide customer-story-container"><img width="350" height="350" decoding="async" src="https://sanday.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Hanneke-Tan.webp" alt="Hanneke-Tan Koning - Medisch Centrum de Weght"/><p>Ik geloof oprecht dat we op weg zijn naar het beste product van Nederland. Sanday is toekomstbestendig en maakt gebruik van de goede dingen van een ander. Maar, het allerbelangrijkste is dat het een platform is dat voor mij werkt.</p><h4>Hanneke-Tan Koning - Medisch Centrum de Weght</h4></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div><div id="klantverhalen-prev" class="swiper-button-prev swiper-nav-button"></div><div id="klantverhalen-next" class="swiper-button-next swiper-nav-button"></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-11 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-top:0px;--awb-background-color:#eae8e3;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-15 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-padding-top:80px;--awb-padding-right:80px;--awb-padding-bottom:80px;--awb-padding-left:80px;--awb-padding-top-medium:16px;--awb-padding-right-medium:16px;--awb-padding-bottom-medium:16px;--awb-padding-left-medium:16px;--awb-overflow:hidden;--awb-bg-color:var(--awb-color1);--awb-bg-color-hover:var(--awb-color1);--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-border-radius:16px 16px 16px 16px;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:-120px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:32px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-margin-top-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-medium:32px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;" data-scroll-devices="small-visibility,medium-visibility,large-visibility"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-end fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-10 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color5);--awb-margin-top:0px;--awb-margin-right:0px;--awb-margin-left:0px;--awb-margin-top-smal